# act configuration for the-journey-of-xoje
#
# We override the default ubuntu image to a Node 22 variant because:
# - pnpm 11 + Node 22 (declared in package.json engines + packageManager)
# - act's default `node:16-bullseye` is too old and fails pnpm install
#
# See: https://nektosact.com/usage/index.html
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest
--container-architecture linux/amd64